@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Returns Policy";
}
<link href="~/assets/css/return.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<div class="returns-container">
    <div class="returns-header">
        <h1>Returns Policy</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="returns-content">
        <p>
            At Elegance, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you are not happy with your items, you can return them in accordance with the policy outlined below.
        </p>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>1. Eligibility for Returns</h2>
            <p>
                You can return items within 30 days of receipt for a full refund or exchange. To be eligible, items must be unworn, unwashed, and in their original condition with all tags attached.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>2. How to Return an Item</h2>
            <p>
                To initiate a return, please contact our customer support team at <strong>returns@elegance.com</strong> with your order number. We will provide you with a return shipping label and further instructions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>3. Refunds</h2>
            <p>
                Once we receive and inspect your returned item, we will notify you of the status of your refund. If approved, your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your original method of payment within 7-10 business days.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>4. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
            <p>
                Certain items, such as undergarments, swimwear, and clearance items, are non-returnable due to hygiene reasons or special conditions. Please check product descriptions before purchasing.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>5. Exchanges</h2>
            <p>
                If you wish to exchange an item, please contact us at <strong>returns@elegance.com</strong>. Exchanges are subject to product availability.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>6. Shipping Costs</h2>
            <p>
                We provide free return shipping for all items. However, original shipping costs are non-refundable, unless the return is due to a defective or incorrect item.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="returns-section">
            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                If you have any further questions regarding our returns policy, please do not hesitate to contact us at <strong>returns@elegance.com</strong> or call us at +1 123-456-7890.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
